<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #6B46C1;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #F9FAFB;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6B46C1;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6B7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your VCC Employment Report</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for registering for the VCC Employment Report. We're excited to share our latest insights into Regional Victoria's employment landscape with you.</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to access your report:</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{reportUrl}}" class="button">Download Report</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>This report includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Detailed regional employment statistics</li>
      <li>Industry-specific insights</li>
      <li>Age demographic analysis</li>
      <li>Policy recommendations</li>
      <li>Success stories and case studies</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>If you have any questions about the report or would like to learn more about our services, please don't hesitate to reach out to our team.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The VCC Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      Virtual Contact Centre<br>
      Supporting Regional Employment
    </p>
    <p>
      <small>
        If you no longer wish to receive our communications, you can 
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">unsubscribe here</a>.
      </small>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
